<br>
4. Where to Level? Ive heard going to Overthere, Lake of Ill Omen, Highpass Hold, and Oasis of Marr. Which would be best in your opinion<br>
<br>
5. Please feel free to add anythign you think might help. This is my first character in EQ and I am loving it.. Ive always been a fan of wizards (in books and whatnot) and I could not see myself as anyything else. Thanks.<br>
